<section class="why-free" id="why-free">
  <div class="why-free__inner">

    <h2 class="why-free__heading">Why is this free?</h2>

    <p class="why-free__body">
      Because we're early. We built the assessment and the report. We haven't run it for 100 local service businesses yet. We're running it for the first ones now, so we can measure what we said would happen against what actually happens, build the case studies, and earn the right to charge for it later.
    </p>

    <p class="why-free__body">
      In exchange for your 12 minutes, you get a written report that tells you specifically what's costing you the most in your business right now, with a dollar number next to each item.
    </p>

    <div class="why-free__anchor">
      <div class="why-free__anchor-row">
        <span class="why-free__anchor-label">What a consultant charges for this</span>
        <span class="why-free__anchor-price">$1,500 – $3,000</span>
      </div>
      <div class="why-free__anchor-row why-free__anchor-row--you">
        <span class="why-free__anchor-label">What you pay</span>
        <span class="why-free__anchor-free">12 minutes</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="why-free__roi">
      If even one of those turns out to be right, the 12 minutes was worth it.
    </p>

    <hr class="why-free__divider" />

    <p class="why-free__closing">
      No pitch on the call. If you want to know what it would cost to fix something we found, ask. We'll tell you. The report is yours to keep, share, or ignore. No follow-up unless you want one. That's not a policy. That's the deal.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-free {
    padding: 80px 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg-section);
  }

  .why-free__inner {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .why-free__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .why-free__body {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .why-free__roi {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(64, 165, 221, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(64, 165, 221, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .why-free__divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  /* Value anchor comparison */
  .why-free__anchor {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .why-free__anchor-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 8px 0;
  }

  .why-free__anchor-row + .why-free__anchor-row {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .why-free__anchor-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .why-free__anchor-price {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-body);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    opacity: 0.6;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .why-free__anchor-free {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pp-sky);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .why-free__closing {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .why-free {
      padding: 64px 20px;
    }

    .why-free__body {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .why-free__roi {
      font-size: 17px;
    }
  }
</style>
